      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "---\n\n**MEMORANDUM**\n\n**To:** New Banking Clients  \n**From:** Compliance Department  \n**Date:** [Insert Date]  \n**Subject:** Know Your Customer (KYC) Compliance Requirements\n\nDear Valued Client,\n\nWe are pleased to welcome you to our banking services. As part of our commitment to regulatory compliance, we require you to provide certain information to help us verify your identity and prevent financial crimes. Please ensure that you have completed the following KYC requirements:\n\n1. **Personal Identification Information:**\n   - Full Name\n   - Date of Birth\n   - Social Security Number (SSN)\n   - Address\n   - Contact Information\n\n2. **Proof of Identity:**\n   - Government-issued photo ID (e.g., driver’s license, passport)\n   - Utility bill or bank statement with your name and address\n\n3. **Verification of Address:**\n   - A recent utility bill, bank statement, or government document with your name and address\n\n4. **Anti-Money Laundering (AML) Compliance:**\n   - Declaration of any previous financial crimes or suspicious activities\n   - Confirmation of the source of funds for any large transactions\n\n5. **Data Privacy and Security:**\n   - Agreement to",
